  Tui3 chit ki5 khi2 sou2 beh lian5-chai3 e5 chong-kau3 siau2-soat “Na7-si7 Chu2 beh chaiN2-iuN7 choe3?” goan5-tu3 si7 ti7 1896 ni5 sia2 e5. Khi2-thau5 si7 ti7 chit8-e5 le2-pai3 am3 e5 chu7-hoe7 chit8 le2-pai3 hoat-piau2 chit8-chiuN,in-ui7 tit-tioh8 toa7 e5 hoan-geng5 chiu7 chhut-pan2 cho3 chit8 pun2 chheh. Goan5-mia5 “Te3 I e5 kha-pou7” (In His steps), ia7 u7 mia5 cho3 “Na7-si7 Chu2 beh chaiN2-iuN7 choe3?” (What would Jesus do?) 
