  Te7 1 Chiunn 
  “In-ui7 Ki-tok ia7 bat ui7 lin2 siu7-khou2, lau5 bou7-iuN7 hou7 lin2, beh hou7 lin2 te3 I e5 kha-pou7”. 
  Pai3-gou7 cha2-khi2, Ma2 bok8-su ti7 i e5 su-chai teh chun2-pi7 to7-li2. I hian-khui Pi2-tek chian5-su 2 chiuN teh thak8, i tit-tioh8 chit8-e5 leng5-kam2, ai3 tui3 “Te3 I e5 kha-pou7” chit chat lai5 kong2-khi2 Ki-tok e5 siu7-khou2, hi-seng, siok8-choe7, soa3 khng3 lang5 oh8 Ki-tok e5 khoan2-sit. I tu2-a2 teh tim5-su ti7 “Te3 I e5 kha-pou7” chit ku3 oe7 sou2 pau-ham5 e5 i3-su3 e5 si5, hut-jian5 tioh8-tioh8 mng5-leng5 teh tan5, i pang3-he7 chhiu2-nih8 sou2 kiah8 e5 pit, kau3 thang-a2 piN khoaN3 tau3-te2 si7 sim2-mih8 lang5-kheh lai5. KhoaN3-kiN3 ti7 mng5-khau2 khia7 chit8-e5 chheng-lian5. Ma2 bok8-su sim-lai7 sui5-si5 kam2-chhiok tioh8 “Ah! Iu7 koh si7 sit-giap8 e5 chheng-lian5 beh lai5 lo5-hoan5 lah!” I chin put-tek-i2 loh8-khi3 chiap-thai7 i. 
  “Ah! bok8-su, goa2 si7 bo5 thau5-lou7 e5 lang5, goa2 siuN7 li2 oe7 hoaN-hi2 pang-bang5 goa2, sou2-i2 goa2 lai5 chhoe7 li2”. Chheng-lian5 khui-chhui3 an2-ni kong2. “Thau5-lou7 chin phaiN2 chhoe7, goa2 ia7 bo5 pan7-hoat thang pang-chan7 li2”, bok8-su kong2 soah chiu7 siuN7 beh koaiN-mng5. 
  “Ah! Bok8-su, li2 kiam2 boe7-thang the3 goa2 sia2 chit8-tiuN kai3-siau7-chng7 hou7 goa2 khi3 thih-lou7 kong-si, a2-si7 kang-tiuN5?” Chheng-lian5 hian2-chhut chin kian3-siau3 e5 khoan2-sit an2-ni kong2. 
  “Bo5 hoat-tou7, goa2 boe7-thang pang-chan7 li2, goa2 cha2-khi2 chin bo5 eng5. Goa2 kho2-lin5 li2, chong2-si7 bo5 pan7-hoat. Goa2 e5 chhu3 ia7 bo5 khiam3 kang, chin sit-le2”. Bok8-su kong2 soah chiu7 koaiN-mng5 khi3, kau3 lau5-teng2 e5 thang-a2 aN3-loh8 bak8-sang3 hit-e5 chheng-lian5, khoaN3 tioh8 chhin-chhiuN7 iap-boe2-kau2 teh kiaN5, chin sit-chi3 e5 khoan2. Bok8-su kau3 i e5 toh-a2, chhoan2 chit8-e5 toa7-khui3 koh ke3-siok8 i e5 chho2-ko2. I kam2-kak chin moa2-i3 ti7 sou2 chun2-pi7 e5. I chin ng3-bang7 le2-pai3-jit8 u7 ho2 e5 thiN-khi3 thang hou7 cheng3 hoe7-iu2 chhut-sek8 lai5 thiaN chit phiN ho2 e5 to7-li2. 
  Le2-pai3-jit8 i2-keng kau3, ko2-jian5 u7 chheng-chheng e5 ho2 thiN-khi3, ti3-kau3 chit-e5 Le7-bun5 chhi7 e5 Te7-it Kau3-hoe7, u7 boan2-tong5 e5 hoe7-iu2 chhut-sek8. Chit-e5 kau3-hoe7 e5 hoe7-iu2 toa7 pou7-hun7 si7 chhi7-lai7 e5 beng5-bong7-ka, chai5-san2-ka. 
  Le2-pai3 taN khai-si2, Seng3-koa-tui7 e5 chan3-bi2 ke-thiN chong-pai3 e5 khi3-hun. In teh gim5, “Goa2 goan7 kun-sui5 Kiu3-chu2 kha-pou7, Eng2 kiaN5 sip8-ke3 to7-lou7, Lou7-tou5 sui-jian5 khi-khu chhiN-sou, Goa2 ia7 bo5 hiam5 kan-khou2.” 
  Seng3-koa-tui7 e5 hap8-chhiuN3 liau2 koh u7 Lah8-kiat sio2-chia2 e5 tok8-chhiuN3. 
  “Goa2 beh toe3 chhin-ai3 e5 Kiu3-chu2, Long2 bo5 hiam5 ho2-phaiN2 e5 keng2-gu7, Pe7 sip8-ke3 kap Chu2 kiaN5 siang7 lou7, Choan-sim te3 Chu2, te3 Chu2 e5 kha-pou7.” 
  Liau5-leng7 bi2-le7 e5 siaN kam2-tong7 mui2 chit8-e5 hoe7-iu2, chun2-pi7 sim thiaN-siu7 bok8-su e5 kang2-to7. Ma2 bok8-su khia7 chiuN7 tai5-teng2, hian-khui i e5 chho2-ko2 khai-si2 i e5 kang2-to7 “Te3 I e5 kha-pou7.” I khoaN3-tioh8 cha2-khi2 u7 chiah-nih8 choe7 e5 hoe7-iu2 chhut-sek8 hou7 i chin moa2-i3. I na2 kong2 na2 lian5-siong2 tioh8 i sou2 bok8-hoe7 chit keng kau3-hoe7 si7 chhi7-lai7 te7-it toa7-keng e5, hou7 i ti7 kang2-tou7 e5 si5, boe7 bian2 ia7 hian2-chhut chin chu7-sin3, chin tek-i3 e5 khoan2-sit. 
  Chong2-si7 tng bok8-su kiat-sok i e5 kang2-to7 che7 loh8-khi3 e5 si5, hut-jian5 u7 chit8-e5 chheng-lian5 kiaN5 kau3 tai5-cheng5. Tai7-ke chin tioh8-kiaN, m7-chai tau3-te2 u7 sim2-mih8 su7 beh hoat-seng. 
  Chheng-lian5 khia7 ti7 tai5-cheng5 tiap8-a2-ku2 chiu7 khui-chhui3 kong2: “Goa2 chin ai3 tui3 lin2 kong2 kui2-ku3 oe7, goa2 chai-iaN2 an2-ni oe7 kiau2-jiau2 lin2 le2-pai3 e5 cheng-sin5, chong2-si7 goa2 choe3-chio2 ti7 goa2 beh si2 i2-cheng5 ai3 chiong goa2 sim-lai7 sou2 ai3 kong2 e5 ka7 lin2 kong2.” 
  Ma2 bok8-su jin7-chhut i chiu7-si7 cheng5-jit8 lai5 chhoe7 i hit-e5 chheng-lian5. 
  “Goa2 si7 chit8-e5 sit-giap8 chia2, chap8-goeh8 jit8 lai5 goa2 chhoe7 bo5 chit-giap8. Chong2-si7 goa2 cha2-khi2 m7-si7 beh kong2 goa2 pun2-sin e5 su7. Goa2 tu2-chiah u7 thiaN-kiN3 bok8-su e5 kang2-to7 “Te3 I e5 kha-pou7”Bok8-su u7 kong2, tioh8 oh8 Chu2 e5 khoan2-sit, chong2-si7 i bo5 soat-beng5 ho2-se3 tau3-te2 si7 beh oh8 sim2-mih8. Goa2 chit 3 goeh8-jit8 ku2, liu5-long7 ti7 ke-bin7, ai3 tit chit-giap8, goa2 tit bo5 tioh8 chit-giap8 ia7 tit bo5 tioh8 chit-ku3 tong5-cheng5 kap an-ui3 e5 oe7. Chi2-u7 chit8-ui7 bok8-su kong2 chin kho2-lin5 goa2, ng3-bang7 goa2 oe7 chhoe7-tioh8 chit-giap8 na7-tiaN7. Goa2 m7-si7 beh kio3 lin2 ka7 goa2 pang-chan7, chi2-u7 hou7 goa2 kam2-kak chin bo5 hah8 e5 chiu7-si7 lin2 chhui3 kong2 “Te3 Chu2 e5 kha-pou7,”gim5 kong2 gia5 sip8-ji7-ke3, chong2-si7 lin2 tau3-te2 oh8 Ki-tok e5 sim2-mih8? Ki-tok ui7 lang5 siu7-khou2 hi-seng, lin2 oh8 sim2-mih8? Kin-a2-jit8 chhi7-lai7 sit-giap8 e5 lang5 u7 500 i2-siong7, toa7-poaN3 u7 ka-teng5 e5 hu7-tam. Chhin-chhiuN7 goa2 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 ti7 4 ko3-goeh8 cheng5 si2 khi3, goa2 e5 soe3-kiaN2 kia3 lang5 chhi7. Goa2 sou2 boe7 beng5-pek8 e5 si7 Ki-tok-tou5 ka-ki7 chhia-hoa5 ian3-lok8, chhui3 koh kong2 “Te3 Chu2 e5 kha-pou7, oh8 Chu2 e5 khoan2-sit”, chong2-si7 in si7 chi2-u7 kiu5 ka-ki7 e5 li7-ek an-lok8. Se3-kan u7 chin-choe7 put-heng7 e5 su7, goa2 siuN7 Ki-tok-tou5 na7 oe7-thang chiau3 sou2 gim5 e5 si te3 Chu2 e5 kha-pou7 oh8 Chu2 e5 khoan2-sit, m7-chai beh kiam2-chio2 loa7-choe7 put-heng7 e5 su7. Lin2 u7 ho2 e5 chhu3 thang khia7, oe7-thang hioh-joah8, hioh-koaN5, chit8 hong-bin7 ti7 pin5-bin5-khut hia u7 loa7-choe7 lang5 ti7 pin5-khou2, choe7-tiong teh seng-oah8......In thong3-khou2, lim-chiu2, choat8-bang7......” 
  Kong2 kau3 chia hit-e5 chheng-lian5 soa3 hun7-to2 ti7 tai5-cheng5. Cheng3 hoe7-chiong3 chhut tioh8-kiaN soan-hoa e5 siaN, bok8-su soan-pou3 le2-pai3 kau3 chia kiat-sok. Sui5-si5 u7 hoe7-iu2 ui5-moa2 tai5-cheng5, u7 i-seng lai5 khoaN3, kong2 si7 sim-chong7 ba5-pi3. Bok8-su kio3 lang5 kng jip8 i e5 kheh-thiaN; ti7 hia chin7-sim chiau3-kou3 i. Chong2-si7 kau3 te7-saN jit8, cheng5-se3 chin bai2, i u7 khui-chhui3 iau-kiu5 lang5 chhoa7 i e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2 lai5 kap i saN-kiN3. Gin2-na2 iau2-boe7 kau3, i chiu7 hian2-chhut boe7-thang koh theng3-hau7 e5 khoan2-sit ka7 bok8-su kong2, “Goa2 boe7-thang kok kiN3 goa2 e5 kiaN2 lah! Kam2-sia7 li2 tui3 goa2 chin chhin-chhiat, goa2 siuN7 Ki-tok ia7-si7 oe7 an2-ni cho3”. Kong2 soah chiu7 tng7-khui3. 
  Le2-pai3-jit8 koh kau3 lah! Ma2 bok8-su e5 bin7 hian2-chhut chin chiau-chui3 e5 khoan2-sit khia7 ti7 tai5-teng2, cha2-khi2 e5 kang2-to7 kap phou2-thong si5 bo5 tang5 e5 sou2-chai7, bok8-su chhin-chhiuN7 u7 chin-choe7 sim-i3 boe7-thang chap8-hun7 kong2-beng5. Kang2-to7 soah, bok8-su kiaN5 kau3 tai5-cheng5, kong2-khi2 cheng5 le2-pai3 sou2 hoat-seng e5 su7. 
  “Lan2 e5 hiaN-ti7, cheng5 le2-pai3 hit-e5 chheng-lian5, i2-keng koe3-ong2. Goa2 m7-chai i e5 keng-lek8, goa2 thiaN kong2 i u7 chit8-e5 chi2-be7 ti7 Chi-ka-ko, goa2 i2-keng sia2 phoe hou7 i, i u7 chit8-e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2 chiam7-si5 siu-liu5 ti7 chia”, bok8-su chhoan2 chit8-e5 khui3, chu3-bak8 khoaN3 hoe7-chiong3 tiap8-a2-ku2 chiu7 koh ke3-siok8 kong2: 
  “Hit-e5 hiaN-ti7 cheng5 le2-pai3 ti7 chia sou2 kong2 e5 oe7 chin kam2-tong7 goa2. Tui3 i hiah-e5 oe7, i2-kip8 i e5 si2, hou7 goa2 chit8-e5 sin e5 bun7-te5, chiu7-si7 “Kun-te3 Ia5-sou” chit-e5 u7 sim2-mih8 i3-su3. Chiau3 lin2 sou2 thiaN hit-e5 hiaN-ti7 sou2 kong2 hiah-e5 si7 tui3 Ki-tok-tou5 e5 chit8-e5 thiau-chian3. Goa2 na2 siuN7 na2 kam2-kak an2-ni. Chit kui2-jit8 lai5 goa2 tui3 chit-e5 bun7-te5, i2-keng u7 siuN7 chhut chit8 e5 hong-hoat. Kin-a2-jit goa2 ai3 chiong chit-e5 hong-hoat pai5 ti7 lin2 e5 bin7-cheng5. Chit-e5 hong-hoat ia7 m7-si7 chit8-e5 sin e5 to7-li2, ia7 m7-si7 chin oh-tit sit8-heng5 e5 hong-hoat, goa2 chin ng3-bang7 lin2 oe7 chap8-hun beng5-pek8 goa2 sou2 beh kong2 e5. “Kun-te3 Ia5-sou!” Lan2 beh chaiN2-iuN7 kun-te3 I? Beh chaiN2-iuN7 te3 I e5 kha-pou7? Goa2 u7 siuN7 chhut chit8-e5 pan7-hoat chiu7 si7 lan2 bo5-lun7 beh cho3 sim2-mih8 su7 i2-cheng5, seng ti7 lan2 e5 sim ka-ki7 mng7 kong2, “Na7-si7 Chu2 beh chai2-iuN7 choe3?” Siat-su2 Chu2 Ia5-sou na7 khia7 ti7 goa2 e5 lip8-tiuN5, i beh chaiN2-iuN7 pan7 chit hang7 su7? Eng7 chit-e5 lai5 choe3 lan2 cho3-su7 e5 chun2-chin5. Liat8-ui7, lin2 thiaN beng5-pek8 mah? Na7 u7 lang5 koat-i3 beh te3 Chu2 e5 kha-pou7, ai3 chiau3 chit-e5 chun2-chin5 lai5 kiaN5 e5 lang5, le2-pai3 au7 chhiaN2 chu7-chip8 ti7 hoe7-gi7-sek”. 
  Hoe7-chiong3 sit8-chai7 chin tioh8-kiaN ti7 bok8-su sou2 kong2 e5, in-ui7 bok8-su kau3-taN sou2 kong2 e5 to7-li2 m7-bat eng7 chit-e5 hong-hoat teh ke2-soeh. Pi3-hoe7 liau2-au7, hoe7-iu2 choe7-choe7 iau2 teh hoe7 sou2 kong2 chit-e5 hong-an3, bok8-su koh chit8 pai2 chhiaN2 u7 koat-i3 e5 lang5 lau5 teh chu7-chip8. Bok8-su kau3 ti7 hoe7-gi7-sek e5 si5 hou7 i tioh8-kiaN, keng2-jian5 u7 4,50 lang5 chu7-chip8. Ki5-tiong ia7 u7 tai7-hak8 chong2-tiuN2 Ma2-si, thih-lou7 pou7-tiuN2 Pa-oa2-su, toa7 siong-giap8-ka Loa7-tek. Oe7-su-tek i-su, siau2-soat-ka Chhoa3-su, chiah-ku2 tit-tioh8 100 ban7 lau7-pe7 e5 ui5-san2 e5 Poe7-ni2 sio2-chia2, i2-kip8 koa-chhiu2 Lah8-kiat. 
  Bok8-su jip8-lai5 chiong mng5 koaiN teh, i e5 bin7 in-ui7 kam2-kek heng-hun3 kau3 chhiN-peh8, i chhui3-tun5 teh chhoah. Si7 lah! In-ui7 chit-e5 hoe7, si7 koan-he7 kau3-hoe7 e5 heng-soe kap i pun2-sin e5 heng-soe. 
  Bok8-su khoaN3-kiN3 chiah-e5 u7 koat-i3 e5 bin7-iong5, chin siu7 kam2-kek. Khi2-thau5 i boe7 hiau2 beh kong2 sim2-mih8, chi2-u7 saN-kap ki5-to2. Seng3-leng5 e5 kam2-hoa3 tui3 ki5-to2, it-hoat chhiong-moa2 ti7 tak8-lang5 e5 sim, Seng3-leng5 e5 leng5-lek8 un7-heng5 ti7 sek-lai7, ki5-to2 soah, tak8 lang5 in-ui7 kam2-kek, thau5-khak iau2-ku2 chhih-chhih, bok8-su e5 bin7 siu7 bak8-sai2 sou2 sip-tam5. I eng7 cheng7-cheng7 e5 gu2-tiau7 khai-si2 kong2: 
  “Lan2 sou2 beh cho3 e5, lan2 long2 beng5-pek8 lah! Lan2 chiu7-si7 bo5 kou3 siuN7 kiat-ko2 chaiN2-iuN7, chi2-u7 siuN7 “Na7-si7 Chu2 beh chaiN2-iuN7 choe3”, lai5 kiaN5 tak8-jit8 e5 seng-oah8, kang-chok. Au7 le2-pai3 goa2 ng3-bang7 oe7-thang tui3 lin2 po3-ko3 goa2 e5 seng-oah8 chiuN7 tui3 chit-e5 u7 toa7 e5 pian3-hoa3. Cheng5 le2-pai3 goa2 na2 siuN7 na2 boe7 moa2-i3 ti7 goa2 cho3 Chu2 e5 hak8-seng e5 khoan2-sit, sou2-i2 goa2 siuN7 chhut chit-e5 pan7-hoat. Goa2 siong-sin3 chit-e5 si7 toa7 koan5-leng5 e5 chhiu2 e5 in2-chhoa7. Lin2 long2 oe7 beng5-pek8 sou2 beh cho3 e5 mah?” 
  “Goa2 ai3 mng7 chit8-hang7” Lah8-kiat sio2-chia2 khui chhui3, cheng3-lang5 e5 gan2-kong chu7-chip8 kau3 i e5 sin-chiuN7.“Goa2 chin hoai5-gi5, chhin-chhiuN7 lan2 chit khoan2 lang5 si7 m7-si7 u7 pan7-hoat thang phoaN3-toan3 sim2-mih8 si7 Chu2 sou2 beh cho3 e5. Na7 u7 m7-chai Chu2 e5 chi2-i3 e5 si5 beh chaiN2-iuN7?” 
  “Si7 lah! Chit-e5 si5 lan2 chi2-u7 kiu5 Seng3 Sin5 e5 pang-chan7, i2-goa7 bo5 pan7-hoat”. 
  “U7-si5 lan2 sou2 khoaN3 e5 phoaN3-toan3 kap pat8-lang5 bo5 tang5 e5 si5 beh chaiN2-iuN7?” Pa-oa2-su mng7. 
  “Si7 lah! Tak8-lang5 e5 kian3-kai2 kiam2-chhai2 boe7-thang long2 saN-tang5, chong2-si7 lan2 na7 u7 seng5-sit8 sim beh chiau3 Chu2 sou2 ai3 cho3 e5 khi3 cho3, goa2 siuN7 boe7-oe7 u7 toa7 e5 chha-piat. Lan2 sou2 m7-thang boe7-ki3-tit e5 chit8-hang7 su7 si7, tng lan2 khak-sit8 phoaN3-toan3 che si7 Chu2 e5 chi2-i3 e5 si5, lan2 tioh8 sit8-heng5, bo5-lun7 kiat-ko2 si7 li7, si7 sun2”. 
  Cheng3-lang5 aN3-thau5 piau2-si7 tong5-i3 ti7 bok8-su sou2 kong2 e5. Tak8-lang5 lip8-iok mui2 le2-pai3 beh chu7-chip8 chit8-pai2 lai5 po3-ko3 tak8-lang5 sou2 le7-heng5 e5 kiat-ko2, bok8-su ki5-to2 pi3-hoe7. Cheng3-lang5 koh chit8-pai2 kam2-kak Seng3-sin5 e5 kam2-hoa3, chiu7 ti7 bu5-gian5 tiong soaN3-hoe7. 
  Bok8-su ka-ki7 koh kau3 ti7 ki5-to2-sek, ki5-to2 poaN3-tiam2 cheng. I iau2 m7-chai Le7-bun5 chhi7 teh beh tui3 chit-e5 su7 siu7 loa7-toa7 e5 eng2-hiong2. 
  Te7 2 Chiunn 
  “KiN3-na7 tiam3 ti7 I e5, tioh8 chiau3 I sou2 kiaN5 e5 lai5 kiaN5.”
  “Le7-bun5 jit8-po3” e5 chu2-pit No2-ni2-bun5, seng-ki5-it chiau3-siong5 chhut-khin5 kau3 sin-bun5-sia7. I u7 chap8-hun e5 koat-sim beh lai5 le7-heng5 cha7-hng e5 se7-iok, chong2-si7 tng i che7-loh8 i e5 toh-a2 e5 si5, i kam2-kak chin tang7-taN3 kap kiaN-hiaN5, i lian5-siong2 kau3 sit8-heng5 chit-e5 se7-iok e5 khun3-lan5 kap sou2 beh hoat-seng e5 chou2-gai7 e5 si5, i kam2-kak chin bo5 khui3-lat8. Na7-si7 oah8-mia7 e5 leng5 ti7 i e5 sim-lai7 cho3-kang, i chiu7 cho3 i kui2-ni5 lai5 m7-bat cho3 e5 su7. Khi2-lai5 koaiN mng5, kui7-loh8 ki5-to2. 
  Tng i kiah8-pit, khai-si2 sia2 sou2 tioh8 sia2 e5 lun7-soat e5 si5, phian-chhip-tiuN2 chhut-siaN kong2: 
  “Che si7 cha7-hng poah8-kiau2 e5 ki3-su7, long2-chong2 u7 3 toaN7-poaN3, siuN7 ai3 long2-chong2 khan-chai3.” 
  “Ho2......oh! ChhiaN2 tan2 leh! hou7 goa2 khoaN3 mai7.” I theh8 hit-e5 eng7 taN2-ji7-ki sou2 taN2 e5 chho2-ko2 lai5 thak8-liau2, chiu7 aN3-thau5 tiam7-tiam7. 
  “Kin-a2-jit8, che m7-thang chhut” theng5 tiap8-a2-ku2 i an2-ni kong2. 
  Phian-chhip-tiuN2 khia7 ti7 mng5-khau2, thiaN-tioh8 chit ku3 oe7 chin tioh8-kiaN koh mng7 kong2 “Li2 e5 i3-su3 si7 kong2 sim2-mih8?” 
  “Che m7-thang khan-chai3.” 
  “Chong2-si7, li2 na7 an2-ni cho3, lan2 e5 thok8-chia2 beh chaiN2-iuN7? Pat8 e5 po3-choa2 long2 u7 khan-chai3, lan2 bo5.” Phian-chhip-tiuN2 chin boe7 beng5-pek8 chu2-pit e5 i3-su3. 
